#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:1
msgid "风控与订单生命周期"
msgstr "Risk control and order lifecycle"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:3
msgid ""
"本章帮您弄清两件事：订单为什么有时「没出去」；出去之后为什么有时一直「部分成交」。重点"
"区分**风控拒单**与**柜台拒单**——这是 live 排错最常见的坑。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter helps you understand two things: why orders sometimes \"don't go "
"through\"; and why, even after going through, sometimes they remain \"partially "
"completed.\" The key difference is between **risk control order rejection** and "
"**counter order rejection**—these are the most common pitfalls in Live troubleshooting."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:5
msgid ""
"亲爱的用户，模拟实盘里「没成交」并不总意味着策略没信号。可能是本地风控拦下了，也可能是"
"模拟券商不收单。我们把两条路径分开讲，您就不会误把风控拒单当成「券商坏了」。"
msgstr ""
"Dear user, \"no trade\" in simulated trading doesn't always mean the strategy isn't "
"sending a signal. It could be that local risk control blocked it, or it could be that "
"the simulated brokerage isn't accepting the order. We'll explain these two paths "
"separately so you won't mistakenly think that risk control rejection means \"the "
"brokerage is malfunctioning.\""

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:7
msgid "0. 适用场景"
msgstr "0. Applicable Scenarios"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:9
msgid "您已能运行 live，但需要判断「未成交 / 拒单 / 撤单」到底发生了什么"
msgstr ""
"You can now run live, but you need to determine exactly what happened in the \"unsold/"
"rejected/cancelled\" cases."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:10
msgid "您想把界面提示、日志与订单状态串成**同一条**可解释链路"
msgstr ""
"You want to link interface prompts, logs, and order status into a **same** explainable "
"chain."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:12
msgid "1. 核心概念：两条「拒单」路径"
msgstr "1. Core Concept: Two \"Order Rejection\" Paths"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:14
msgid "很多用户第一次遇到拒单，会以为「都是券商拒的」。在 qteasy 里，请先分清："
msgstr ""
"Many users, when encountering order rejections for the first time, assume \"they're "
"all rejected by brokerage firms.\" In qteasy, please first clarify:"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:24
msgid ""
"在 live 子系统中，订单从策略信号到最终成交须经过 **RiskManager（可选）→ 本地建单 → "
"Broker 受理 → 成交回报** 几站。下表归纳三种结局——排错时请先对号入座「类型」列，再按「优"
"先查哪里」打开对应日志。"
msgstr ""
"In the live subsystem, an order goes through several stages from strategy signal to "
"final execution: **RiskManager (optional) → Local order creation → Broker processing → "
"Execution report**. The table below summarizes three possible outcomes—when "
"troubleshooting, first match the category to the \"Type\" column, then click \"First "
"check which part\" to open the corresponding log."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:26
msgid ""
"**各列含义**：**类型**为路径名称；**您会看到什么**为界面/返回值特征；**订单表有记录吗**"
"指本地 `sys_op_trade_orders` 是否新增行；**优先查哪里**为建议的第一份证据。"
msgstr ""
"**Column Meanings**: **Type** is the path name; **What You Will See** is the interface/"
"return value characteristic; **Is There a Record in the Orders Table?** indicates "
"whether a new row has been added to the local `sys_op_trade_orders`; **Where to Check "
"First** is the first piece of evidence for the suggestion."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:28
msgid ""
"**如何使用**：CLI 出现英文 `Order rejected by risk rule` → 选「风控拒单」行 → 查 "
"`risk_log`；订单列表里有 `rejected` 且无 broker 号 → 选「柜台受理拒单」行。"
msgstr ""
"**How to use:** When the CLI displays \"Order rejected by risk rule\", select the "
"\"Risk Rejection\" line and check the \"risk_log\". If the order list contains "
"\"rejected\" and no broker number, select the \"Counter Rejection\" line."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "类型"
msgstr "Type"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "您会看到什么"
msgstr "What will you see?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "订单表有记录吗"
msgstr "Is there a record in the order form?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "优先查哪里"
msgstr "Where to search first"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**风控拒单**"
msgstr "**Order rejection due to risk control**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "CLI 英文拒因；提交结果为空 `{}`"
msgstr "CLI rejection reason (English); Submission result is empty `{}`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**没有**新行"
msgstr "**No new lines**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
