msgstr "Maximum 500 shares"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "要买 501 股 → **拒绝**；500 股且其他通过 → **放行**"
msgstr ""
"Request to buy 501 shares → **Rejected**; 500 shares and other requests approved → "
"**Proceeded**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "交易时段"
msgstr "Trading Hours"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "仅 9:30–11:30、13:00–15:00"
msgstr "Only from 9:30–11:30 and 13:00–15:00"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "午休下单 → **拒绝**"
msgstr "Orders placed during lunch break → **Rejected**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
