msgstr "What should you pay attention to?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**submitted**"
msgstr "**submitted**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "柜台已收单，尚未全部成交"
msgstr ""
"The counter has received the orders, but not all transactions have been completed."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "是否有 `broker_order_id`"
msgstr "Does it have a `broker_order_id`?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**partial-filled**"
msgstr "**partial-filled**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "部分成交，累计量 < 委托量"
msgstr "Partial transactions completed, cumulative volume < order volume."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "累计成交量是否在增加"
msgstr "Is the cumulative trading volume increasing?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**filled**"
msgstr "**filled**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "累计成交量达到委托量"
msgstr "The cumulative transaction volume reached the order volume"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "持仓与现金是否已更新"
msgstr "Have your holdings and cash balances been updated?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**canceled**"
msgstr "**canceled**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "已撤单"
msgstr "Order cancelled"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "收盘或手动撤单后的终态"
msgstr "Final state after market close or manual order cancellation"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**rejected**"
msgstr "Often `rejected`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "柜台受理阶段拒绝"
msgstr "Refusal during counter service stage"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "broker 号通常为空；**不是**风控拒单"
msgstr ""
"The broker number is usually empty; **this is not** a risk control order rejection."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:110
msgid "**排查思路**："
msgstr "**Investigation Approach**:"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:111
msgid "「根本没有 submitted」→ 先查风控与提交前校验（§1 表）"
msgstr ""
"\"No submissions were submitted\" → First check the risk control and pre-submission "
"verification (§1 Table)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:112
msgid "「一直是 partial-filled」→ 查成交回报是否在持续到达（§4）"
msgstr ""
"\"Always partially filled\" → Check if the transaction returns are continuously "
"arriving (§4)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:114
msgid "4. 分批成交与全部成交"
msgstr "4. Partial transactions vs. full transactions"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:116
msgid ""
"当一笔大单分多笔成交时，状态会先停在 **partial-filled**，像「委托只成交了一部分」。   "
"当**累计成交量达到委托数量**时，qteasy 会将状态更新为 **filled**。若您看到长期 partial-"
"filled，请对照成交回报与目标数量——有时只是行情或模拟撮合尚未凑满整单。"
msgstr ""
"When a large order is split into multiple transactions, the status will initially "
"remain at **partial-filled**, like \"Only part of the order has been filled.\" Once "
"the **cumulative transaction volume reaches the target order quantity**, Qteasy will "
"update the status to **filled**. If you see a prolonged period of **partial-filled** "
"status, please compare the transaction data with the target quantity—sometimes it "
"simply means that market conditions or demo matching haven't yet filled the entire "
"order."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:119
msgid "5. 收盘后未成交订单"
msgstr "5. Unfilled orders after market close"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:121
msgid "收盘后，qteasy 会通过 `post_close` 任务统一收尾当日未决订单："
msgstr ""
"After the market closes, qteasy will use the `post_close` task to close all pending "
"orders for the day."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:123
msgid ""
"**`submitted` / `partial-filled`**：视为曾进入柜台，收盘撤余量，终态为 **`canceled`**"
"（可能有撤单成交记录）。"
msgstr ""
"**`submitted` / `partial-filled`: This indicates that the order was submitted to the "
"counter, and the remaining amount was withdrawn at the close. The final state is "
"**`canceled` (there may be cancellation transaction records)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:124
msgid ""
"**`created`**：视为未成功报单的本地草稿（如报单链路中断或历史遗留），收盘置为 "
"**`rejected`**，**不**与盘中柜台拒单混淆，也**不**写入撤单型成交结果。"
msgstr ""
"**`created`:** This is considered a local draft of an unsuccessful order (e.g., an "
"interrupted order placement process or a legacy issue). It is set to **`rejected`** at "
"the close of trading. It should not be confused with intraday order rejections, nor "
"should it be written into the cancellation transaction results."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:126
msgid ""
"对您而言：收盘后请关注 `post_close` 相关日志与 `reconcile` 对账输出，确认在途单是否已按"
"规则收尾，而不必记忆内部 API 名称。"
msgstr ""
"For you: After the market closes, please check the `post_close` logs and `reconcile` "
"reconciliation outputs to confirm whether orders in transit have been closed according "
"to the rules, without having to remember the internal API names."

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md:128
msgid "6. 遇到异常时建议顺序"
msgstr ""
"6. When encountering an anomaly, it is recommended to proceed in the following order."

